data.description: Gorgeous, move-in ready remodel in the heart of Tulsa. This home features all NEW flooring, lighting, fixtures, HVAC and granite counters throughout. Three updated bathrooms, updated kitchen with all new appliances. Neutral paint colors and finishes throughout. Off the entry is a dedicated dining room or flex space. Living room with painted brick, wood burning fireplace and grey accent wall. Eat-in kitchen, laundry room, flex space, ensuite primary and two bedrooms on the main floor. Game room/flex space, one spacious bedroom with ensuite bathroom upstairs. Garage has cabinets for extra storage. Fully fenced large backyard in a quiet and convenient location, close to The Farm Shopping Center, LaFortune Park, St. Francis Hospital, Expressways, Shopping. (Owner/Agent)
